et is suitable for the\ndetection of low flux and/or monoenergetic type electron/positron signals with\nfinite transverse sizes. It offers unparalleled advantages for gammaray\nspectroscopy in the intermediate MeV range.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Apr 2019 16:13:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Apr 2019 14:41:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-14"}
