 baryon density is reached in the cavity, a necessary condition for the\noperation of the \"inner engine\" of the GRB presented in an accompanying article\n(Ruffini & Moradi 2019).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Apr 2019 17:12:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Jun 2019 11:17:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 5 Jul 2019 16:34:11 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 18 Jul 2019 16:07:02 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 6 Aug 2019 21:49:37 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Sun, 11 Aug 2019 16:10:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-07"}
