ate applicability of our methodology\non several examples and numerical case-studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Apr 2019 20:23:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 May 2020 02:45:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-21"}
