r scenario than the internal bar\nbuckling perturbation scenario as the origin of the phase space mixing. Origin\nof the more prominent snail shell in the $V_{\\phi}$ color-coded phase space is\nalso discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Apr 2019 22:58:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Jun 2019 09:05:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 12 Sep 2019 10:17:25 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 15 Jan 2020 09:33:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-26"}
