r ($<$10$^4$ yr) for high\n$G$$_{\\mathrm{0}}$ PDRs. By contrast, inner regions reach equilibrium much\nlater, especially low $G$$_{\\mathrm{0}}$ PDRs, where steady state is reached at\n$\\sim$10$^6$-10$^7$ yr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Apr 2019 11:42:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-17"}
